pt;\">企业合作项目</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>  <td width=\"57\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">7</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"255\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">典型移动音视频业务质量研究</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"142\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">2004,9-2005,9</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"112\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">企业合作项目</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>  <td width=\"57\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">8</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"255\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">H.264</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">编解码算法的</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">Intel</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">平台优化</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"142\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">2004.11-2006.11</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"112\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">企业合作项目</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>  <td width=\"57\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">9</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"255\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">基于</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">Trimedia TM1302</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">H.264</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">解码器</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"142\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">2005,7-2005,11</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"112\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">企业合作项目</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>  <td width=\"57\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">10</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"255\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">H.264 CIF</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">解码优化及错误隐藏</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"142\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">2006.1-200.6</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"112\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">企业合作项目</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>  <td width=\"57\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">11</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"255\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">低码率数字音频压缩算法的质量与评价</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"142\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Verdana, sans-serif;\">2006.8-2006.11</span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"112\">  <p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\">企